me.utk.util.function.lambda

Interface Lambda3<R,T1,T2,T3>

  • Type Parameters:
    R - The return type of this lambda function
    T1 - The type of parameter 1 for this lambda function
    T2 - The type of parameter 2 for this lambda function
    T3 - The type of parameter 3 for this lambda function
    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface Lambda3<R,T1,T2,T3>
    Represents a lambda function which takes in 3 parameters and returns an object of type R.

    The types of the 3 parameters are T1, T2, and T3, respectively.

    This is a FunctionalInterface whose functional method is get(Object, Object, Object).

    Version:
    December 10, 2020
    Author:
    Utkarsh Priyam
